Package: DEEPSPACE
Type: Package
Title: Syntenic analysis and plotting from genome assemblies
Version: 0.1.0
Author: John T. Lovell
Maintainer: John T. Lovell <jlovell@hudsonalpha.org>
Description: Treats genomic 'windows' similarly to peptides and runs the 
    GENESPACE alignment and synteny calling method on these. 
Imports: Biostrings, 
  GenomicRanges, 
  Rsamtools, 
  data.table,
  dbscan,
  ggplot2
SystemRequirements: MCScanX, 
  minimap2
